<br>
robe of abatement: AC8 sta/cha1 int5 SVD/P5<br>
robe of asylum: AC10 sta/cha4 int9 HP10 mana 15 SVD/P8<br>
robe of misery: AC11 sta/cha6 int11 HP25 mana 25 SVD/P10<br>
 focus: affliction efficiency III<br>
robe of obligation: AC9 sta/cha2 int6 SVD/P6<br>
robe of requisition: AC9 sta/cha3 int8 HP10 mana 10 SVD/P8<br>
robe of tenancy: AC10 sta/cha5 int10 HP15 mana 20 SVD/P9<br>
<br>
all robes weigh 0.0 and are race all / class NEC WIZ MAG ENC<br>
<br>
what von and i need are:<br>
maneater buds, which drop off of certain flower mobs in swamp of no hope and are also foraged there;<br>
honey berry, which drop off drolvargs (in my experience - they may drop off other mobs, too) and are foraged in dreadlands;<br>
words of abatement, asylum, misery, obligation, requisition or tenancy - whichever you want us to make<br>
<br>
right now we have quite a few honey berries, but we really need maneater buds.<br>
<br>
i'm not sure von and i have worked out a full price list for these robes for federation members.  right now ishkandele (my bazaar bot) still has a few robes of abatement and requisition.  let me know if you're interested in one and i'll talk to von about price.  the prices i have those for on ishkandele are way higher than what they will be for fed members.  the hardest part about making these robes, really, is getting a high-level researcher to make the swatches out of the words (most of the research trivials are in the 160 to 180 range).  if you can help with that or know someone who'd be willing to help we can work something out.  so far von has handled getting the swatches made, so you might want to talk to him if you'd like some sort of compensation.<br>
<br>
i'd like to point out that only one of these robes is trivial to me, so there's a chance i may not succeed with the combine (the focus effect robe is 250 + in tailoring), but hopefully the random number generator will be on my side when i do the combines.<br>
